ComicInfo.Summary:
Fatal Furry: Lynn challenges Britanny to a fight.
The Shun Goku Satsu of Love!: Lynn and Pee Wee's minions fight it out in the library.
Guest in the Machine: An elaborate ploy captures three criminal leaders.
Showdown in Aisle 7: Gina and Brit run afoul of a toy collector.
Return of the Lich King: The Lich King has a plan to return to his former glory.
